| 3 | **Medium** | Add `prefers-reduced-motion` handling for the slide-in animation |
| 4 | **Low** | Add ARIA landmark (`role="complementary"`) to the detail panel wrapper |
| 5 | **Low** | Extract 40% to a shared Sass token |

